Luke Genovesi Music

Melbourne based musician and guitar teacher, exploring sounds of Blues, Rock, Jazz and Fusion

My Mission

 
 

I have been playing guitar for over 15 years. My goal is to inspire and mentor you in painting your own musical picture. My modern and intellectual approach to the many aspects of the guitar will help to find your own voice with the instrument. I am honoured to start this creative journey with you.
